    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "At this pool how clear the picture"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Of the hopeless case of all"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Who are seeking self-perfection"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To recover from the fall."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Though the law is good and holy,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Flesh, to keep the law, is dead;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What we need is not religion,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But the Word of life instead."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Though it’s feast day, he’s not happy,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Though the Sabbath, there’s no rest;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lying in his poor condition,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Miserable and sore depressed."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "At that moment Jesus saw him,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Knowing he was thus so long."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Will you be made whole?” He asked him,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Healed and walking, well and strong?”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Though he told his hopeless story,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Scarce believing what he’d heard,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet, soon to his feet arising,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He received the living word."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This is all our situation,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We—like him—were lying there"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the sheep-fold of religion,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Under law’s prevailing care."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "While we yet were weak and helpless,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ the Son of God did come."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By His word we’re now enlivened;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s the life-imparting One!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Hallelujah for this Jesus,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s the Word of life to men;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "From law’s bondage He releases,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Death is turned to life again!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    }
  ],
